<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us | Air Quality Project</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="container header-content">
        <a href="home" class="home-button">Home</a>
        <h1 class="header-title">About Our Air Quality Initiative</h1>
        <p>
          Committed to delivering accurate, accessible air quality information
          worldwide
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
      <section class="about-hero">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
          Founded in 2025, our air quality project began as a response to the
          growing need for transparent, real-time pollution data. What started
          as a small team of environmental scientists and data enthusiasts has
          grown into a global platform serving millions of users each month.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mission-section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We believe everyone has the right to breathe clean air and access
          reliable information about their environment. Our mission is to
          empower individuals, communities, and policymakers with accurate air
          quality data and tools to understand pollution's impact on health and
          climate.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="values-section">
        <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
        <div class="value-cards">
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Accuracy</h3>
            <p>
              We source data from trusted providers and rigorously validate all
              information before publication.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Accessibility</h3>
            <p>
              We design our tools to be usable by everyone, regardless of
              technical expertise.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Transparency</h3>
            <p>
              We clearly document our data sources and methodologies for full
              accountability.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Impact</h3>
            <p>
              We measure our success by the positive changes our users make with
              our data.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="data-sources-section">
        <h2>Our Data Sources</h2>
        <p>
          We partner with leading data providers to deliver the most accurate
          air quality information
        </p>
        <div class="data-source-logos">
          <div class="data-source-item">
            <img
              src="media/open_weather.png"
              alt="OpenWeather"
              class="data-source-logo"
            />
            <a
              href="https://openweathermap.org/"
              class="resource-link"
              target="_blank"
              >OpenWeather</a
            >
          </div>
          <div class="data-source-item">
            <img src="media/waqi.jpeg" alt="WAQI" class="data-source-logo" />
            <a href="https://waqi.info" class="resource-link" target="_blank"
              >World Air Quality Index</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/resources" class="resources-button">Explore All Resources</a>
      </section>
    </div>

